PRIVACY POLICY
Last updated: January 06, 2025

This Privacy Policy for Kingpin ("we," "us," or "our") outlines how we collect, use, share, and protect your personal information when you interact with our services ("Services"). This includes when you:

Download and use our mobile application (Kingpin) or any other application that links to this Privacy Policy.
Engage with us in other related ways, including through sales, marketing, or events.
If you have any questions or concerns, please contact us at thekingpinshoes@gmail.com or call us at +91-8090009443.

SUMMARY OF KEY POINTS
This summary highlights key points from our Privacy Policy. For more details, refer to the corresponding sections.

What personal information do we collect?
We collect personal information you provide directly (e.g., name, email, phone number) and data from other sources (e.g., public databases).

Do we collect sensitive personal information?
No, we do not process sensitive personal information such as racial or ethnic origin or religious beliefs.

Do we share your information?
We share information only in specific situations, such as business transfers or to comply with legal requirements.

How do we keep your information safe?
We employ technical and organizational measures to safeguard your information but cannot guarantee 100% security due to inherent internet risks.

What are your rights?
You have rights depending on your location, such as accessing, updating, or deleting your personal data.

