1. What Information Do We Collect?
Personal Information You Provide to Us
We collect personal information you voluntarily provide when registering, contacting us, or using our Services. This includes:

Names
Phone numbers
Email addresses
Contact preferences
Information From Third Parties
We may collect additional data from public databases, marketing partners, and social media platforms to improve our services and marketing strategies.

2. How Do We Process Your Information?
We process your information to:

Facilitate account creation and authentication.
Respond to user inquiries and provide support.
Fulfill and manage orders, payments, and returns.
Improve our services and ensure security.
3. When and With Whom Do We Share Your Personal Information?
We may share your personal information:

During business transfers, such as mergers or acquisitions.
To comply with legal obligations or enforce our policies.
4. How Long Do We Keep Your Information?
We retain your information only as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy or as required by law. When no longer needed, we securely delete or anonymize your data.

5. How Do We Keep Your Information Safe?
We use reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission or storage is entirely secure, so we cannot guarantee complete security.

6. Do We Collect Information From Minors?
We do not knowingly collect data from children under 18. If we become aware of such collection, we will delete the data promptly.

7. What Are Your Privacy Rights?
Depending on your location, you may have the right to:

Access and review your personal information.
Update or delete your data.
Withdraw consent where applicable.
8. Controls for Do-Not-Track Features
We do not currently respond to "Do Not Track" signals as no standard has been established.

9. Do We Make Updates to This Policy?
Yes, we may update this policy as necessary to stay compliant with laws. Updates will be indicated by the "Last updated" date at the top of this document.

10. How Can You Contact Us?
If you have questions, please contact us via email at thekingpinshoes@gmail.com or by mail at:

